review_title: DO NOT BUY - want my money back
one_reviews_text: I can't get a single song to play, like.. nothing.. every song I click on says failure to load, it's not blocked on my end, there are rooms, I have a failure to open a room, create a room, or view room list. It tells me to add my own music to go to music youtube and I go there, and I already have playlists created but yet, nothing shows up in the app.. do not buy
review_feedback:
Please check the 1.0.6 update.
We apologize for any inconvenience.

one_reviews_text: I seem to have seen a new way of VR content. It was a very interesting and good experience. If you follow the pictures in the tutorial, you can play the music without problems.
